reviewText: This is a rated R movie, all sex scenes were cut to the core. beside the picture was not clear, and the story was very weak.
Okay movie for the time it was made in; wouldn't stand the test of time though... Story is razor thin and there is no acting to speak of.

1) Picture quality is bad.  2) Nudity and Story do not draw much attention.  3) "R" rating to these two movies.  Stimulating sex scenes.
4) For real sex scenes, viewers can hardly see anything in this video.
